/*
Find position of an element in an infinite sorted array. This question is not possible to to do it on an editor. It's just the idea that is asked.
*
*/


Solution: - 

int binarySearch(int arr[], int x)
{
    int start=0;
    int end=1;
    while(arr[end]<x)
    {
        start=end;
        end=end*2;
    }
    SimpleBinarySearch(start,end,x);         //Created another file for simple binary search...
}
